Paipo, penjahat Paipo.

24
00:02:35,648 --> 00:02:39,547
Tinju Shaolin Hooligan.

25
00:02:39,548 --> 00:02:42,347
Itu Paipo, Shuringan Paipo.

26
00:02:42,348 --> 00:02:44,647
Gurindai Shuringan.

27
00:02:44,648 --> 00:02:47,647
Popokopi dan Ponpokona Gurindai.

28
00:02:47,648 --> 00:02:51,347
Sekarang, namanya Chokyumei Chosuke.

29
00:02:51,348 --> 00:02:52,747
Mouri,

30
00:02:52,748 --> 00:02:55,347
